<owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="#evidence113">
  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#Evidence"/>
  <evidenceContent rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">COPPA Children Online Privacy Protection Act When it comes to the collection of personal information from children under 13 the Children s Online Privacy Protection Act COPPA puts parents in control The Federal Trade Commission the nation s consumer protection agency enforces the COPPA Rule which spells out what operators of websites and online services must do to protect children s privacy and safety online</evidenceContent>
